summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Lane Street, from a point 120 feet west of Twentieth Avenue South to Rainier Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing a sewer under Ordinance No. 19008, creating Local Improvement District No. 1816 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
